components.name: Extract AirVisual Data
components.description: Fetches current air quality and weather data from the AirVisual API for the configured latitude/longitude, checks PostgreSQL for existing records to avoid duplicates, and writes the response atomically to /opt/airflow/data/tmp_airvisual.json.

upstream_policy.description: First component in the pipeline; no upstream dependencies.

connections.purpose: PostgreSQL data warehouse for duplicate detection and later loading

components.name: Validate AirVisual JSON
components.description: Reads the JSON file generated by the extraction step, validates its structure and required fields, and logs confirmation before downstream processing.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful extraction of AirVisual data.

components.name: Load AirVisual Data to PostgreSQL
components.description: Transforms the validated AirVisual JSON into a dimensional model and inserts records into PostgreSQL dimension and fact tables using idempotent upserts (ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING).
outputs: Rows inserted into dimDateTimeTable, dimLocationTable, dimMainPollutionTable, factairvisualtable

upstream_policy.description: Executes after successful validation of the AirVisual JSON.

connections.purpose: Target PostgreSQL data warehouse for dimensional loading

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

LATITUDE.description: Latitude coordinate for the AirVisual API request

LONGITUDE.description: Longitude coordinate for the AirVisual API request

timeout_seconds.description: Maximum time (in seconds) to wait for the API response

api_key_config_path.description: Path to configuration file containing the AirVisual API key

json_file_path.description: Path to the JSON file generated by the extraction step

mapping_main_pollution_path.description: Path to JSON file mapping main pollution codes

mapping_weather_code_path.description: Path to JSON file mapping weather codes

timezone.description: Timezone used for datetime conversion (Bangkok timezone, UTC+7)

sources: AirVisual API (nearest_city endpoint) providing current air quality and weather data
sinks: PostgreSQL data warehouse tables: dimDateTimeTable, dimLocationTable, dimMainPollutionTable, factairvisualtable
